s_cryst: READ FILE=../COLVAR_sc EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=s_cryst
ses_O2: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=ses_O2
metad: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=metad.rbias
lwall_sws_C3: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=lwall_sws_C3.bias
uwall_sws_C3: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=uwall_sws_C3.bias
lwall_sws_O2: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=lwall_sws_O2.bias
uwall_sws_O2: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=uwall_sws_O2.bias
lwall_sws_C9: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=lwall_sws_C9.bias
uwall_sws_C9: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=uwall_sws_C9.bias
lwall_ses_O2: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=lwall_ses_O2.bias
uwall_ses_O2: READ FILE=../2-COLVAR EVERY=1 IGNORE_TIME VALUES=uwall_ses_O2.bias

weights: REWEIGHT_METAD TEMP=300 ARG=metad.rbias,lwall_sws_C3.bias,uwall_sws_C3.bias,lwall_sws_O2.bias,uwall_sws_O2.bias,lwall_sws_C9.bias,uwall_sws_C9.bias,lwall_ses_O2.bias,uwall_ses_O2.bias

HISTOGRAM ...
 ARG=s_cryst,ses_O2
 GRID_MIN=0.0,0.0
 GRID_MAX=1.0,1.0
 GRID_BIN=120,120
 BANDWIDTH=0.1,0.1
 LOGWEIGHTS=weights
 LABEL=hh
... HISTOGRAM

DUMPGRID GRID=hh FILE=histo FMT=%24.16e STRIDE=0

CONVERT_TO_FES GRID=hh LABEL=FES_temp TEMP=300

DUMPGRID GRID=FES_temp FILE=fes_reweighted.dat STRIDE=50000

